\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{2}^{*}$
\end_inset

 which are OLS residuals of regressing 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{2}$
\end_inset

 on 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{1}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

